[SN]TITLE[SN]
Groom stands for bride in wedding vow surprise

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Bridegroom Neil Martin, who has a rare form of muscular dystrophy, surprised his wife-to-be Ginny Marchmont by taking his wedding vows standing up.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is unsupported on your device
2 August 2015 Last updated at 10:28 BST
Mr Martin raised the money for a stand-up wheelchair but didn't tell her he planned to use it at the ceremony in Westbury in Wiltshire.
